WESTERN NORTH ATLANIC.
RHODE ISLAND TO NORFOLK.
DNC 17.
43 FOOT VESSEL CAROL K, WHITE HULL, ONE PERSON
ON BOARD, OVERDUE JAMESTOWN (41-31N 071-22W) TO
NORFOLK (36-55N 076-12W). VESSELS IN VICINITY
REQUESTED TO KEEP A SHARP LOOKOUT, ASSIST IF
POSSIBLE. REPORTS TO RCC NORFOLK,

E-MAIL: RCCNORFOLK@USCG.MIL.
